SELECT `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Address`, `t`.`ContactDetails`, `t`.`CreatedAt`, `t`.`Email`, `t`.`TotalAmount`, `t0`.`Id`, `t0`.`BookId`, `t0`.`OrderId`, `t0`.`OrderPrice`, `t0`.`Quantity`, `t0`.`SubscriptionId`, `t0`.`Id0`, `t0`.`BookDate`, `t0`.`BookDescription`, `t0`.`BookImage`, `t0`.`BookName`, `t0`.`Price`, `t0`.`Id1`, `t0`.`SubDescription`, `t0`.`SubPrice`, `t0`.`SubType`
FROM (
    SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`
    FROM `Order` AS `o`
    WHERE `o`.`Id` = @__newOrder_Id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t0` ON `t`.`Id` = `t0`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id`, `t0`.`Id`, `t0`.`Id0`

FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`
FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`
FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`

    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`

) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`

FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`
FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`
FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`
FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
WHERE (((`o`.`Email` IS NOT NULL AND (LOWER(`o`.`Email`) LIKE @__search_0_contains)) OR (`o`.`ContactDetails` IS NOT NULL AND (LOWER(`o`.`ContactDetails`) LIKE @__search_0_contains))) OR (`o`.`Address` IS NOT NULL AND (LOWER(`o`.`Address`) LIKE @__search_0_contains))) OR (CAST(`o`.`Id` AS char) LIKE @__search_0_contains)
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`

CREATE TABLE `Accounts` (
    `Id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
    `Username` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `Password` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `Email` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `SubscriptionId` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `Role` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `contactDetails` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `Address` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `Active` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `Block` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `SubcriptionStart` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `SubcriptionEnd` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `CreateAt` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `Token` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `TokenExpiry` datetime(6) NULL,

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`
FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`
FROM `Order` AS `o`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `o0`.`Id`, `o0`.`BookId`, `o0`.`OrderId`, `o0`.`OrderPrice`, `o0`.`Quantity`, `o0`.`SubscriptionId`, `b`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `b`.`BookDate`, `b`.`BookDescription`, `b`.`BookImage`, `b`.`BookName`, `b`.`Price`, `s`.`Id` AS `Id1`, `s`.`SubDescription`, `s`.`SubPrice`, `s`.`SubType`
    FROM `OrderItems` AS `o0`
    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t` ON `o`.`Id` = `t`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `o`.`Id`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`
